mat.\n\n---\n\nclass: inverse, center, middle\n\n# Importing and exploring data\n\n---\n\n# Importing data in R\n\n```{r eval=FALSE, tidy=FALSE}\nmydata <- read.csv(\"/directoryname/filename.csv\")\n\nmydata <- read.table(\"/directoryname/filename.csv\",\n                     sep = \",\",\n                     header = TRUE)\n\nmydata <- read.csv(file.choose()) ## No recommended!      \n```\n\n---\n\n# Importing data in R\n\n```{r tidy=FALSE, message=FALSE, warning=FALSE}\n\n# data ----\nmydata <- read.csv(\"Exercise/data/Survey_data_clean.csv\")\n\nstr(mydata)\n\nlevels(mydata$Sex)\n\n```\n\n---\n\n# Exploring your data\n\n```{r tidy=FALSE, message=FALSE, warning=FALSE}\n\n# data ----\nmydata <- read.csv(\"Exercise/data/Survey_data_clean.csv\", \n                   stringsAsFactors = FALSE,\n                   strip.white = TRUE,\n                   na.strings = c(\"NA\",\"\"))\nstr(mydata)\n\nunique(mydata$Sex)\n\n```\n\n---\n# Exploring your data\n\n```{r tidy=FALSE, message=FALSE, warning=FALSE}\n\n# libs ----\nlibrary(tidyverse)\n\n# data ----\nmydata <- read_csv(\"Exercise/data/Survey_data_clean.csv\")\n\nmydata\n```\n\n---\n\n# Exploring your data\n\n```{r tidy=FALSE, message=FALSE, warning=FALSE}\nclass(mydata$Sex)\n\nlevels(mydata$Sex)\n\nunique(mydata$Sex)\n```\n\n---\n\n# Exploring your data\n\n```{r tidy=FALSE, message=FALSE, warning=FALSE}\nmydata$Sex<-factor(mydata$Sex, levels=c(\"F\",\"M\"))\n\nclass(mydata$Sex)\n\nlevels(mydata$Sex)\n```\n\n---\n\nclass: inverse, center, middle\n\n# Manipulating data\n\n\n---\n\n# Data carpentry \n\n\n",
